<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3  hidden-sm hidden-xs">
    <img src="/img/LOGO vertical - SJPL SRC.png" class="home-bot">
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 hidden-xs">
  <br/><br/>
    <h4>Accept the Challenge!</h4>
    <p>The San Jos√© Public Library challenges people of all ages to spend time reading, learning, exploring, and energizing during the summer.</p>
    <p>Play games! Earn great prizes! Attend free events! And prevent yourself (or your children) from slipping down the summer slide!</p>
    <h4>Prevent the Summer Slide</h4>
    <p>During summer break, students who do not spend time reading and learning can find their school year skills slipping backwards. Teachers and literacy experts agree that reading for <strong>20 minutes per day</strong> during the summer helps students retain their skills and return to school ready to learn.</p>
 
    <h4>Read as a Family</h4>
    <p>The Library also challenges you to share the joy of reading as a family. Everyone from the baby to great-grandpa can get involved! Reading for pleasure is one of the building blocks needed for young people to grow into healthy, productive adults.</p>

      <div class="text-left">
          <div class="fb-share-button" data-href="http://www.sjplsummer.org" data-layout="button"></div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12">
          <div class="panel panel-sr margin-10">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">Sign In</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <form role="form" method="post" action="/accounts/signin">
                  <% if(typeof flash.error() != 'undefined') { %>
                    <div class="row">
                        <span class="text text-danger">&nbsp;&nbsp; <%=flash.error()%></span>
                    </div>
                  <% } %>
                  <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="accountName">User&nbsp;Name</label>
                      <%- contentTag('input', params['accountName'], {name: 'accountName', id: 'accountName', class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'User Name', tabindex: '1'});%>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="accountName">PIN (4 digits)</label>
                      <%- contentTag('input', params['passcode'], {name: 'passcode', id: 'passcode', type: 'password', class: 'form-control', placeholder: '4 digit pin', tabindex: '2'});%>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" tabindex="3">Sign&nbsp;In</button>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <a href="/accounts/register" class="link" alt="First time users, Click here to register" tabindex="4">Create&nbsp;New&nbsp;Account</a>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 margin-10">
        <iframe width="425" height="239" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/fjcnAy3oXtI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
